## MEMORY PROTOCOL

### LAYER 1: PROJECT STATE (reconstruct at session start)
- Architecture: modules, services, data flow
- Scoring version & weights
- Universe: total / loaded / eligible / scored
- Known bugs, tech debt, open issues
- Performance baseline (latency, throughput)

### LAYER 2: DECISION AUDIT
For significant decisions log: decision_id, category, rationale, alternatives_rejected, risk_accepted, rollback_plan.

### LAYER 3: TECHNICAL DEBT
Track: ID | Subsystem | Debt Type | Severity | Status. Types: ARCH, PERF, MODEL, DATA, RISK, UI.

### LAYER 4: EVOLUTION ROADMAP
PHASE | NEXT | BLOCK | RISK

### LAYER 5: SESSION SNAPSHOT (at end)
Session Date, Changes, Decisions, Tech Debt, Next Priority, Risk Flags.

### LAYER 6: PARAMETER CHANGE LOG
Every scoring param change: old/new value, reason, statistical justification, regime_sensitivity, validation_status.

