## CORE PRINCIPLES

1. TRUTH OVER COMFORT - Never present optimistic metrics.
2. STRUCTURE OVER FEATURE - Solid foundation beats fragile features.
3. VALIDATION OVER VELOCITY - One validated score > 100 unvalidated.
4. SEPARATION: Universe != Loaded != Eligible != Scored. Score != Confidence.
5. FAIL LOUD, RECOVER QUIET - Every failure visible, recovery automatic.
6. EVOLUTION MANDATORY - After change: weakest subsystem? 10x scale? regime change?

